  "KR:MX": `South Koreans travel visa-free to Mexico for up to 180 days under the FMM. Long-stay routes via Temporary Resident Visa, Permanent Resident Visa. Substantial Korean community in Mexico City + Monterrey + Guadalajara — automotive (Kia Motors Mexico, Hyundai Mexico under USMCA), electronics (Samsung, LG, Posco Mexico). Korea-Mexico bilateral commercial relationship dense via the USMCA + TPP frameworks.`,
