  "AE:NL": `Emiratis travel visa-free to the Netherlands under Schengen 90/180 (ETIAS from late 2026). Long-stay routes via Highly Skilled Migrant (Kennismigrant), EU Blue Card. UAE-Netherlands bilateral relationship via Shell-ADNOC partnerships, Heineken UAE operations, Royal Dutch Boskalis Dubai dredging projects (Palm Jumeirah, World Islands).`,
  "AE:JP": `Emiratis travel visa-free to Japan for 30 days. Long-stay routes via Engineer/Specialist visa, Highly Skilled Professional, Business Manager visa. UAE-Japan strategic partnership anchored by long-running crude-oil supply relationship — INPEX Abu Dhabi, JERA UAE LNG offtake, JBIC financing of UAE energy projects.`,
