  "IL:JP": `Israelis travel visa-free to Japan for 90 days. Long-stay routes via Engineer/Specialist visa, Highly Skilled Professional, Business Manager visa. Growing Israeli community in Tokyo + Osaka — heavy tech-sector concentration (Israeli cybersecurity + AI startups acquired by SoftBank, Sony, Rakuten), reciprocal Japanese investment in Israeli VC ecosystem.`,
  "IL:KR": `Israelis travel to South Korea — K-ETA waived for Israeli passport holders. Long-stay routes via E-7 specialty-occupation, D-8 corporate investor, F-6 marriage visa. Growing Israeli community in Seoul — tech sector (Israeli cybersecurity + AI acquired by Samsung-LG Korean conglomerates), reciprocal Korean tech investment in Israel.`,
